- Data processing and database access
- Web Server
---
- **Automation Script**
- Shell / Bash / PowerShell
- Task scheduling, backups
- OS
{% /table %}

---

### **In Summary**

> Scripting languages make the web *come alive.*\
JavaScript powers the browser,\
PHP and Python power the server,\
and Node.js unites them under a single language.

Together, they form the **programmable heart of the modern web**, enabling developers to create intelligent, interactive, and efficient web systems.
